%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20swapped%20my%20gas%20truck%20for%20a%20Chinese%20hybrid.%20The%20BYD%20Shark%20is%20great%20to%20drive%2C%20but%20one%20thing%20worries%20me.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221456%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Wayne%20Dopson%20BYD%20Shark%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F681c757fc6ad288d148057e3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221092%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDopson%20bought%20his%20BYD%20Shark%20pickup%20for%2064%2C000%20Australian%20dollars%20(%2441%2C000).%3Cp%3EWayne%20Dopson%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EWayne%20Dopson%20runs%20a%20renovation%20business%20in%20Brisbane%2C%20Australia%2C%20and%20bought%20a%20BYD%20Shark%20hybrid%20pickup%20in%20March.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20said%20it's%20great%20to%20drive%20compared%20with%20his%20old%20gas%20truck%2C%20but%20fears%20it%20may%20be%20obsolete%20in%20a%20few%20years.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EChinese%20EV%20makers%20are%20expanding%20rapidly%20in%20tariff-free%20Australia%2C%20putting%20Tesla%20under%20pressure.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Wayne%20Dopson%2C%20a%20project%20manager%20in%20Brisbane%2C%20Australia%20about%20owning%20a%20BYD%20Shark%20hybrid%20pickup%20truck.%20It%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20always%20been%20in%20the%20property%20market%2C%20flipping%20houses%20and%20doing%20renovations.%20I%20have%20a%20small%20renovation%20business%2C%20working%20on%20kitchens%2C%20bathrooms%2C%20and%20decks%20for%20clients%20in%20Brisbane%2C%20which%20I've%20been%20doing%20for%20about%2012%20years%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20bought%20a%20VW%20Amarok%20diesel-powered%20pickup%20in%202015.%20I%20wanted%20to%20upgrade%20for%20a%20while%2C%20but%20nothing%20came%20along%20that%20took%20my%20interest.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20combustion-engine%20trucks%20like%20the%20Ford%20Ranger%20were%20all%20very%20similar%20to%20the%20Amarok.%20I%20would%20have%20been%20getting%20pretty%20much%20the%20same%20car%20with%20just%20a%20bigger%20screen%2C%20so%20I%20waited%20for%20something%20a%20little%20bit%20different.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20bought%20the%20BYD%20Shark%20hybrid%20pickup%20in%20March%20for%2064%2C000%20Australian%20dollars%2C%20around%20%2441%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFord%20and%20Toyota%20are%20charging%20ridiculous%20prices%20for%20their%20pickup%20trucks%2C%20or%20utes%20in%20Australia.%20You're%20looking%20at%20up%20to%2080%2C000%20dollars%20for%20something%20that%20is%2C%20to%20me%2C%20inferior%20to%20what%20BYD%20is%20charging%2060%2C000%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20only%20done%202%2C000%20kilometers%20in%20the%20Shark%20so%20I'm%20still%20learning%20the%20car%2C%20but%20so%20far%20I%20love%20driving%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20technology%2C%20the%20power%2C%20and%20the%20smoothness%20%E2%80%94%20it%20feels%20decades%20ahead%20of%20the%20Amarok.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d6daab6a-c5ec-4a75-82a5-aa5464dd4927%5C%22%3ELuxury%20and%20power%20on%20the%20cheap%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20level%20of%20luxury%20inside%20is%20incredible%20for%20the%20money.%20I've%20owned%20Audis%20and%20BMWs%20and%20it%20feels%20just%20as%20good%2C%20just%20as%20solid%20and%20well-built%20as%20a%20premium%20car.%20It%20also%20does%200%20to%20100km%2Fh%20in%205.7%20seconds%2C%20so%20it%20drives%20like%20a%20sports%20car.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221458%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22BYD%20Shark%20interior%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F681e1e49a466d2b74ab58424%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221084%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDopson%20said%20the%20BYD%20Shark's%20interior%20was%20luxurious.%3Cp%3EWayne%20Dopson%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20use%20it%20mainly%20for%20work%20as%20well%20as%20leisure%2C%20and%20there%20are%20a%20couple%20of%20advantages%20to%20using%20it%20for%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20costs%20me%20just%20cents%20to%20run%20it%20each%20day.%20I've%20got%2030%20solar%20panels%20on%20my%20roof%2C%20so%20my%20electricity%20during%20the%20day%20is%20free.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20pay%20eight%20cents%20per%20kilowatt%20hour%20from%2012%20a.m.%20to%206%20a.m.%2C%20which%20is%20enough%20time%20to%20charge%20the%20car%20%E2%80%94%20it%20takes%20between%20three%20to%20four%20hours%20to%20charge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20I%20set%20the%20car%20to%20charge%20at%20midnight%2C%20it's%20done%20by%20about%204%20a.m.%2C%20and%20it%20generally%20costs%20less%20than%20two%20Australian%20dollars%2C%20or%20%241.03.%20I'd%20be%20using%2013%20or%2014%20dollars%20(%248-9)%20worth%20of%20diesel%20a%20day%20in%20the%20VW%20Amarok%2C%20so%20comparatively%20it's%20very%20cheap%20to%20run.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20advantage%20is%20you've%20got%20power%20outlets%20in%20the%20back%20of%20the%20truck%20that%20provide%20about%20six%20kilowatts%20of%20power%2C%20which%20you%20can%20use%20on-site%20to%20power%20tools.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22BYD%20Shark%20ports%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F681c75cdc6ad288d148057ee%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Shark's%20power%20sockets%20can%20be%20used%20for%20appliances%20and%20tools.%3Cp%3EWayne%20Dopson%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20got%20a%20really%20big%20tray%20with%20a%20couple%20of%20little%20tricks%20up%20its%20sleeve.%20You%20can%20open%20your%20tailgate%20with%20a%20quick%20press%20of%20the%20key%2C%20which%20is%20handy%20if%20you're%20walking%20up%20with%20your%20hands%20full.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e86a559f-db8e-43d0-bc4b-809e19521389%5C%22%3ERange%20is%20not%20a%20problem%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Shark%20is%20what%20they%20call%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fextended-range-electric-vehicles-erev-gas-generator-range-anxiety-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEREV%2C%20or%20extended%20range%20electric%20vehicle%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It's%20got%20two%20electric%20motors%2C%20at%20the%20front%20and%20rear%2C%20and%20it%20also%20has%20a%201.5-liter%20petrol%20turbo%20engine%20that%20acts%20as%20a%20generator.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20petrol%20engine%20means%20range%20anxiety%20isn't%20really%20a%20thing%20for%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGenerally%2C%20I%20do%20less%20than%20100%20kilometers%20a%20day%2C%20which%20will%20be%20done%20in%20electric%20mode%2C%20but%20if%20I%20do%20want%20to%20go%20to%20the%20beach%20or%20further%20down%20the%20coast%2C%20I've%20got%20the%20petrol%20engine%20right%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20just%20kicks%20in%20and%20charges%20the%20battery%20and%20I'm%20good%20to%20go%20for%20around%20800%20kilometers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20only%20thing%20that%20would%20worry%20me%20down%20the%20line%20is%20the%20resale%20value.%20I've%20already%20seen%20that%20new%20vehicles%20are%20coming%20out%20from%20Nissan%2C%20Ford%2C%20and%20Great%20Wall.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20technology%20is%20advancing%20like%20crazy%20at%20the%20moment%2C%20so%20my%20Shark%20could%20be%20fairly%20obsolete%20in%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20got%20a%20six-year%20warranty%2C%20and%20I'm%20planning%20to%20keep%20it%20for%20the%20warranty%20period.%20What's%20it%20going%20to%20be%20worth%20at%20the%20end%20is%20anyone's%20guess.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2282512d3d-61a0-44d5-b4de-7cb1bbf46995%5C%22%3EBYD%20puts%20down%20roots%20in%20Australia%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20having%20more%20Chinese%20EV%20brands%20in%20Australia%20is%20great.%20We're%20getting%20longer%20warranty%20periods%20and%20better%20quality%20cars.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22BYD%20Shark%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F681c75f2a466d2b74ab55ab0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDopson%20uses%20the%20Shark%20for%20his%20renovation%20business%20in%20Brisbane.%3Cp%3EWayne%20Dopson%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EUtes%20are%20a%20very%20important%20part%20of%20Australian%20culture.%20One%20of%20the%20issues%20the%20BYD%20Shark%20will%20face%20is%20that%20it%20doesn't%20have%20the%20same%20off-roading%20credentials%20as%20a%20vehicle%20with%20a%20diff%20lock%20%E2%80%94%20an%20axle%20mechanism%20that%20you%20need%20to%20crawl%20over%20rocks%20and%20rough%20terrain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20fine%20on%20the%20sand%20and%20in%20the%20mud%2C%20but%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20really%20serious%20off-roading%2C%20where%20you%20are%20crawling%20up%20huge%20hills%20with%20ruts%20and%20boulders%2C%20it's%20going%20to%20struggle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20me%2C%20though%2C%20the%20Shark%20is%20great.%20It's%20a%20pleasure%20to%20drive%2C%20and%20it's%20nice%20being%20able%20to%20drive%20around%20knowing%20it's%20not%20costing%20me%20and%20not%20costing%20the%20planet%20either.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fswapped-gas-truck-for-hybrid-byd-shark-2025-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1746937261000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F681e22343fe8d39283656c62%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fswapped-gas-truck-for-hybrid-byd-shark-2025-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Wayne%20Dopson%2C%20who%20swapped%20his%20gas%20truck%20for%20a%20Chinese%20hybrid%2C%20loves%20his%20new%20BYD%20Shark%20but%20is%20concerned%20about%20it's%20resale%20value%20in%20a%20couple%20years.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22tcarter%40businessinsider.com%20(Tom%20Carter)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fswapped-gas-truck-for-hybrid-byd-shark-2025-5%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Walton%20Goggins%20Uses%20His%20%E2%8