or%20Baldoni%20has%20backed%20down%20in%20their%20legal%20battle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20August%202024%20premiere%20of%20%26quot%3BIt%20Ends%20With%20Us%2C%26quot%3B%20based%20on%20Colleen%20Hoover's%20eponymous%20book%2C%20Lively%20filed%20a%20complaint%20with%20the%20California%20Civil%20Rights%20Department%20accusing%20Baldoni%20of%20sexually%20harassing%20her%20and%20creating%20a%20%26quot%3Bhostile%20work%20environment%20that%20had%20nearly%20derailed%20production%20of%20the%20Film.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20complaint%20also%20accused%20Baldoni%20and%20his%20team%20of%20attempting%20to%20damage%20Lively's%20public%20reputation.%20The%20complaint%2C%20formalized%20into%20a%20lawsuit%20last%20December%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftaylor-swift-hailey-bieber-blake-lively-complaint-justin-baldoni-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ementioned%20Swift%20by%20name%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjustin-baldoni-libel-lawsuit-against-nyt-blake-lively-story-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBaldoni%20sued%20The%20New%20York%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20libel%20last%20December%20after%20the%20outlet%20published%20an%20article%20about%20Lively's%20accusations.%20One%20month%20later%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjustin-baldoni-sues-blake-lively-ryan-reynolds-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBaldoni%20accused%20Lively%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20her%20husband%2C%20Ryan%20Reynolds%2C%20of%20taking%20over%20the%20film%20and%20attempting%20to%20hurt%20his%20reputation%20in%20a%20%24400%20million%20lawsuit.%20Both%20Lively%20and%20Reynolds%20have%20asked%20for%20Baldoni's%20lawsuit%20to%20be%20dismissed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftaylor-swift-witness-blake-lively-justin-balboni-lawsuit-2025-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3