here%20as%20a%20Christian%20Black%20woman%2C%20but%20my%20tune%20has%20changed.%20I've%20surprised%20myself%20with%20how%20much%20I%20like%20it%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22625cc1d9-05dd-462f-ad06-e0593cc21f89%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThere%20were%20things%20about%20Riyadh%20that%20surprised%20me%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20my%20husband%20already%20had%20friends%20living%20in%20Riyadh%2C%20finding%20an%20apartment%20wasn't%20hard.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20first%20year%2C%20we%20rented%20an%20apartment%2C%20but%20we%20live%20in%20a%20compound%20now%20because%20it's%20closer%20to%20where%20my%20husband%20works.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EExpats%20tend%20to%20flock%20to%20compounds%20because%20there%20are%20no%20dress%20restrictions%20and%20there%20are%20amenities.%20Europeans%2C%20Americans%2C%20and%20people%20from%20all%20over%20the%20world%20live%20in%20a%20compound%2C%20which%20is%20a%20bit%20pricer%20than%20a%20normal%20apartment.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20some%20other%20expats%20want%20to%20live%20with%20the%20locals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20first%20things%20I%20had%20to%20come%20to%20terms%20with%20was%20that%20Riyadh%20is%20heavily%20reliant%20on%20cars%20and%20driving%2C%20so%20most%20locals%20don't%20rely%20on%20public%20transport.%20The%20Riyadh%20Metro%20Station%20opened%20last%20year%2C%20which%20is%20quite%20popular%2C%20but%20you%20still%20have%20to%20drive%20to%20the%20metro.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20London%2C%20I%20would%20dedicate%20my%20Saturday%20mornings%20to%20walking%20around%20the%20town%20and%20grabbing%20a%20coffee%20on%20the%20way%20back.%20You%20can't%20really%20do%20that%20here%20because%20there%20aren't%20as%20many%20places%20around%20as%20in%20London.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Saudi%20government%20is%20trying%20to%20add%20more%20greenery%2C%20but%20it's%20not%20really%20a%20walkable%20city%20yet.%20It's%20too%20hot%20to%20walk%20half%20the%20year%20anyway%20because%20temperatures%20can%20reach%20113%C2%B0F.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20was%20how%20to%20dress.%20When%20you%20hear%20about%20Saudi%20Arabia%2C%20you%20might%20think%2C%20%26quot%3BOh%2C%20I%20need%20to%20buy%20a%20scarf%20or%20wear%20an%20Abaya.%26quot%3B%20You%20don't%20need%20to%20do%20that%20as%20an%20expat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20not%20Muslim%20or%20if%20you're%20not%20from%20Saudi%20Arabia%2C%20there%20are%20no%20expectations%20to%20cover%20up%20like%20the%20locals%20do.%20You%20can%20wear%20whatever%20you%20want%20as%20long%20as%20you%20are%20dressed%20modestly%20and%20respectful%20of%20the%20culture.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20Saudis%2C%20or%20people%20who%20live%20in%20Riyadh%2C%20are%20Muslim%2C%20so%20it's%20embedded%20in%20the%20culture%2C%20and%20you%20will%20hear%20prayer%20calls%20all%20day.%20During%20Ramadan%2C%20many%20stores%20are%20closed%20during%20the%20day%20because%20people%20are%20fasting.%20The%20local%20coffee%20shop%20will%20be%20open%20from%20about%207%20p.m.%20to%202%20a.m.%2C%20which%20I%20hadn't%20experienced%20before.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EBeing%20Christian%2C%20it%20kind%20of%20encouraged%20me%20to%20take%20my%20faith%20more%20seriously%20because%20they%20take%20theirs%20very%20seriously.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20the%20workweek%20in%20Saudi%20Arabia%20is%20Sunday%20to%20Thursday.%20I%20still%20get%20confused%20sometimes%2C%20and%20it's%20taken%20me%20a%20while%20to%20adjust%20to%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%20the%20biggest%20impact%20that%20it's%20had%20on%20my%20life%20is%20that%20my%20mental%20health%20is%20much%20better%20here.%20It's%20not%20like%20I%20hated%20the%20UK%2C%20but%20I%20always%20had%20seasonal%20depression.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20was%20winter%20in%20London%2C%20I%20never%20wanted%20to%20leave%20the%20house%2C%20but%20I%20don't%20have%20any%20of%20that%20here.%20Even%20during%20the%20winter%20in%20Riyadh%2C%20it's%20always%20sunny.%20It's%20improved%20my%20quality%20of%20life%20and%20mental%20health.%20I%20just%20feel%20lighter%20here.%20Especially%20coming%20from%20the%20corporate%20world%20in%20London%2C%20where%20everything's%20quick.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220a408be2-2691-4b04-b8ee-688de0e0f45f%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ERiyadh%20is%20a%20modern%20city%20that's%20continuing%20to%20grow%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ERiyadh%20has%20grown%20since%20I%20first%20visited.%20My%20husband%20and%20I%20have%20met%20more%20expats%20in%20the%20last%20six%20months%20than%20ever%20before.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20has%20something%20called%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsaudi-arabia-vision-2030-projects-trillion-value-neom-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESaudi%20Vision%202030%3C%2Fa%3E.%20They're%20trying%20to%20make%20Saudi%20Arabia%20a%20top%20travel%20destination%2C%20so%20they've%20introduced%20lots%20of%20new%20entertainment.%20There%20are%20lots%20of%20boxing%20matches%20now%2C%20and%20last%20year%2C%20we%20hosted%20a%20tennis%20tournament%20with%20Rafael%20Nadal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20visit%2C%20you%20will%20be%20surprised%20how%20much%20you%20like%20Saudi%20Arabia.%20There%20are%20so%20many%20things%20tourists%20can%20do%2C%20like%20visiting%20the%20museums%20or%20Boulevard%20World%2C%20which%20has%20exhibitions%20of%20different%20countries%20showcasing%20the%20food%20and%20culture.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESaudi%20Arabia%20is%20much%20more%20modern%20than%20people%20give%20it%20credit%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frelocating-to-riyadh-saudi-arabia-quality-of-life-mental-health-2025-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1746891177000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F681e3f633fe8d392836573cf%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frelocating-to-riyadh-saudi-arabia-quality-of-life-mental-health-2025-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Banke%20Adebola%20left%20London%20and%20moved%20thou