r%20confidence%20in%20the%20J-10C.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJordan%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BYou%20may%20well%20see%20a%20very%20viable%20competitor%20to%20Western%20products%20entering%20contests%20for%20the%20purchase%20of%20new%20fighter%20aircraft%2C%26quot%3B%20added%20Jordan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20could%20pose%20a%20challenge%20for%20Western%20defence%20manufacturers%2C%20he%20added.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20J-10C%20is%20not%20China's%20most%20advanced%20fighter%20%E2%80%94%20that%20distinction%20belongs%20to%20the%20fifth-generation%20stealth%20J-20%20%E2%80%94%20it%20may%20well%20be%20the%20most%20commercially%20viable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-j10-fighter-jet-f-16-pakistan-air-force-2025-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1746882638000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F681f17893fe8d392836583d7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-j10-fighter-jet-f-16-pakistan-air-force-2025-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22China's%20J-10C%20fighter%20was%20deployed%20by%20Pakistan%20against%20India%20this%20week%20and%20may%20become%20a%20%26quot%3Bvery%20viable%20competitor%26quot%3B%20to%20western%20rivals%2C%20one%20expert%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22rrommen%40insider.com%20(Rebecca%20Rommen)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A360%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-j10-fighter-jet-f-16-pakistan-air-force-2025-5%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20helped%20my%20daughter%20get%20a%20job%20at%20my%20company%20after%20her%20college%20graduation.%20Sometimes%2C%20I%20regret%20it%20and%20wonder%20if%20I%20set%20her%20up%20for%20failure.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224555%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22two%20women%20in%20the%20office%20sitting%20at%20a%20desk%20and%20looking%20at%20computer%5C%