%20or%20groceries.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20I%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoving-from-new-york-to-charlotte-north-carolina-surprising-things-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Emoved%20from%20NYC%20to%20North%20Carolina%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20my%20steps%20plummeted.%20I%20started%20working%20from%20home%2C%20and%20most%20days%20I%20was%20clocking%20less%20than%201%2C000%20steps%20in%20a%20day.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20started%20feeling%20sluggish%20and%20gross%20for%20moving%20so%20little%20throughout%20the%20week%20and%20decided%20to%20look%20into%20getting%20a%20walking%20pad.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt's%20been%20almost%20two%20years%20since%20I%20got%20mine%2C%20and%20I%20still%20use%20it%20to%20get%20between%208%2C000%20to%2010%2C000%20steps%20(or%20sometimes%20more)%20a%20day.%20A%20few%20things%20have%20helped%20keep%20me%20motivated%20to%20stick%20with%20it.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221a4009af-53c0-4280-a2d8-854016fd0c2a%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20knew%20I%20wouldn't%20use%20a%20walking%20pad%20that%20wasn't%20easy%20to%20set%20up%20and%20put%20away%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Walking%20pad%20below%20a%20raised%20desk%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6818df763fe8d3928364ecd9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIt%20was%20critical%20for%20me%20to%20pick%20an%20option%20that's%20as%20easy%20as%20possible%20to%20take%20out%20and%20put%20away.%20%3Cp%3EElliott%20Harrell%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20knew%20I%20wouldn't%20be%20likely%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftreadmill-desk-walking-pad-not-worth-it-year-later-review-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%