b505e2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWorking%20while%20I%20walk%20makes%20me%20focus%20more%20on%20the%20task%20at%20hand.%3Cp%3EElliott%20Harrell%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EProbably%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20reasons%20I've%20continued%20using%20my%20walking%20pad%20for%20so%20long%20is%20that%20it%20makes%20me%20feel%20better%20during%20the%20day.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20I%20start%20to%20feel%20like%20I'm%20in%20a%20slump%2C%20walking%20for%20even%20a%20few%20minutes%20gets%20me%20out%20of%20it.%20%3C%2Fspan%3EDaily%20movement%20like%20this%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Ffitness%2Fbenefits-of-walking%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egood%20for%20my%20health%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20helps%20me%20feel%20more%20energized.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPlus%2C%20I've%20found%20it%20can%20help%20meetings%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20ones%20where%20I'm%20more%20of%20just%20a%20listener%20than%20a%20participant%20%E2%80%94%20go%20by%20more%20quickly.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20I'm%20walking%2C%20I%20feel%20more%20locked%20in%20on%20whatever%20task%20is%20at%20hand%2C%20and%20it's%20harder%20to%20step%20away%20from%20my%20desk%20and%20get%20distracted%20by%20something%20else.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAll%20in%20all%2C%20my%20walking%20pad%20has%20been%20a%20game%20changer%20for%20getting%20my%20steps%20in%20and%20for%20helping%20me%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-be-more-productive-at-work-take-breaks-2017-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ebe%20more%20productive%20at%20work%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20I%20can't%20see%20a%20world%20where%20I%20ever%20stop%20using%20it.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flove-treadmill-desk-benef