At%20SOF%20Week%202025%2C%20the%20company's%20CEO%2C%20Bryan%20Bockmon%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20about%20how%20the%20company%20is%20now%20focusing%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffuture-warfighting-decisions-inhuman-speeds-air-force-secretary-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eautonomous%20weapons%20systems%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20may%20be%20crucial%20for%20future%20warfare%2C%20systems%20made%20for%20defeating%20drones.%20Countering%20drones%20is%20an%20expanding%20area%20of%20research%20and%20development%2C%20with%20a%20lot%20of%20work%20being%20done%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20though%20that%20isn't%20the%20only%20country%20where%20this%20technology%20is%20being%20developed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-drone-defense-tech-industry-warfare-russia-attacks-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EUkraine%20war%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20shown%20that%20electronic%20warfare%20like%20signal%20jamming%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fair-force-teaching-ai-to-navigate-aircraft-gps-is-gone-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGPS%20spoofing%3C%2Fa%3E%20can%20be%20effective%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20defeating%20enemy%20drones%2C%20but%20having%20a%20kinetic%20option%2C%20the%20ability%20to%20shoot%20it%2C%20as%20a%20last%20resort%20for%20destroying%20those%20systems%20is%20essential%20should%20other%20options%20fail.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20they%20may%20fail%20because%20some%20drones%2C%20like%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-unjammable-fiber-optic-drone-keep-pace-russia-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efiber-optic%20drones%3C%2Fa%3E%20becoming%20more%20common%20in%20Ukraine%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraines-smart-drones-more-likely-hit-targets-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI-enabled%20systems%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20are%20resistant%20to%20electro