20AimLock's%20development%20approach%20interesting%20is%20that%20%26quot%3Binstead%20of%20making%20specialized%20systems%20that%20then%20have%20to%20be%20reinvented%2010%20times%20over%20to%20cover%20the%20entire%20mission%20need%2C%26quot%3B%20Bockmon%20said%2C%20it%20makes%20%26quot%3Bgeneralized%20modules%20that%20can%20be%20adapted%20across%2010%20different%20missions.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222516%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20automated%20machine%20gun%20points%20out%20towards%20the%20blue%20ocean%20with%20a%20blue%20sky%20in%20the%20background.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F681e828ec6ad288d14809832%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221398%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECounter-UAS%20systems%20are%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20industry%20conversations%20right%20now%20as%20DoD%20pushes%20for%20more%20capabilities.%3Cp%3EAimLock%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20if%20the%20warfighter%20needs%20a%20different%20sensor%20or%20weapon%20system%2C%20it%20can%20find%20an%20AimLock%20product%20to%20match.%20It%20reduces%20the%20development%20cycle%2C%20the%20CEO%20said%2C%20lowering%20costs%20and%20simplifying%20the%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company's%20Core%20Targeting%20Module%2C%20or%20CTM%2C%20as%20it's%20called%2C%20is%20at%20the%20heart%20of%20AimLock's%20systems.%20It%20combines%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-allies-ai-target-enemies-like-would-war-first-time-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eautonomy%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20firing%20and%20targeting%20components%20to%20improve%20the%20speed%20and%20precision%20of%20weapons%20from%20guns%20to%20uncrewed%20systems.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20CTM%20hardware%20is%2C%20in%20some%20cases%2C%20just%20a%20small%20black%20box%20with%20a%20few%20plug-in%20outlets%20on%20top.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBockmon%20said%20the%20modularity%20of%20it%20and%20other%20weapons%20systems%20AimLock%20makes%20allows%20it%20%26q